r-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">专业的推荐：</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">汉语言文学专业尽量选相近的，西洋语文学虽然看着很像，但是实际上简称西语系，课程及教学内容存在较大差距。</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvN1fQK1iaI9UTC4pRPiaibp9KbqTsuoCC3doJAm8tWrgbibXyPSNNsvNA1w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" class=\"\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.66600790513834\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvN1fQK1iaI9UTC4pRPiaibp9KbqTsuoCC3doJAm8tWrgbibXyPSNNsvNA1w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 733.6px; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">Summer:</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">大陆学校：东北林业大学</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">旅游管理专业</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">台湾学校：国立屏东大学</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">休闲事业经营与管理学系</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">交换生活将近一半～对台湾的新鲜感与好奇心也渐渐消</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">失…台湾没什么好的，做交换生也没什么特别，但就是不想离开，不想结束这段日子…不矫情了，毕竟我是正能量小公举哈哈～总之，你来就对了</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">现在想想当时面试还是挺简单的。我先是一分钟自我介绍，主要就是讲自己和别人不一样的大学经历啊什么的，总之就是把自己一顿夸，特别淡定自信的那种[害羞]关键是不要紧张，我们学校面试的时候有四个老师，然后就看着我对面的老师的眼睛开始一顿吹～其实也都是事实哈哈，把老师看的都不好意思了你就赢了。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">申请通过之后就是老师让我们办各种手续，该办什么老师到时候就会通知的。我印象比较深的就是办通行证的时候，要在办证的地方照相，五官什么的都要露出来，最重要的是不能带隐形，我那天也没有带眼镜盒，现买的矿泉水在一堆人面前抠眼睛，也是彻底醉了～</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">最后说说我的专业吧，我学旅游管理的，来台湾是休闲系的～总之我是特别爱我的专业哈哈 选学校的时候先看看有没有合适自己的专业，我当时看的台北大学，东海大学什么的都没有和自己专业相关的科系，屏东大学的休闲事业经营管理学系和我的专业比较相符就直接报的这个～事实证明没有选错，上课方式和内容和大陆的完全不一样，因为有陆生的缘故，不管哪门课，老师总会问一些关于大陆的问题，这个时候就会感叹，两岸人民对彼此的了解真是太浅薄了～</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">屏东在台湾南部，比较乡下的感觉，人们的生活节奏慢慢慢慢…人情味也是足足的，或许在这些地方你又能体会到大多数人体会不到的台湾哈哈～反正我是超满意的 刚来的时候学校给陆生办欢迎会，班导师还会组织班游～对陆生也是超好的 可以说是有求必应 有的科系会给陆生安排学伴，学伴是台湾学生，有什么问题学伴都会帮忙解决，有的学伴还会带陆生到处吃东西玩耍～</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">总之，不管别人眼中怎么看交换生，在台湾的日子一定会让自己倍加珍惜经历过的点点滴滴～</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：soda--rain</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvicLdcfUEkmcUU6VibW1y8BibIZHMr74ibyx5RtZAlvPA2rEfb2cibBgPqibA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" class=\"\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.66600790513834\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvicLdcfUEkmcUU6VibW1y8BibIZHMr74ibyx5RtZAlvPA2rEfb2cibBgPqibA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 733.6px; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.04px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">北方姑娘：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3:学校各种盖章交文件我就说了，因为每个学校都不一样。说一下去国台办办批件，要注意批件下来的时间为半个月左右。重点是拿到了批件以后就必须在一个月以内去公安局办大通证(紫色小本)。办理这个也需要提前预约，不同省份进度不同。不过应该都在一个周以内。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">很多同学申请批件以后就回家了。没多久批件下来了。又因为有时间限制，所以还得中途赶回学校所在地去办大通证。所以要注意这个时间。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(22, 100, 4);\">渔舟唱晚：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1，不要有偏激太过强烈的政治主张。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、准备一张城市本地的银行卡，如长沙银行，重庆银行之类的比华夏银行还好用任何时候取款任何一比都免汇率哦。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、申请台北以外的学校物价会低些，至少不会闹水果蔬菜荒，哈哈。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、在台北的话雨伞，拖鞋最好自己备好过来，这边的丑而贵，雨伞也不便宜且没有天堂伞好用。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：Solitary_hx</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvG0AJkict5aF0N6oFn92crGJ5EZUZPR7iaqDw56VaTHicB2ic6xhibxEA2xg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7509881422924901\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"677px\" class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvG0AJkict5aF0N6oFn92crGJ5EZUZPR7iaqDw56VaTHicB2ic6xhibxEA2xg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(6, 117, 11); font-family: inherit; font-size: 19.04px; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 1.6;\">盐焗肘子：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.我的学校是用绩点和面试成绩综合排名来选学校，面试比重较大。在面试之前我有参加过一个月东吴大学组织的的夏令营，对台湾有初步认识，这个为我增分很多，同时找到台湾同学了解学校学分设置，课余时间看一些关于台湾历史的书，这样能让老师觉得我不其他人做的功课更多，面试时也能游刃有余。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.前期材料确实需要准备很多，特别是当你没有本地户口还需要一些反复手续。材料大致分两部分，一是完成台湾学校的申请，台学校会帮办入台证（那张纸），二是拿到批件后去办大陆这边发的大通证。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3.在买机票时需要大通证证件号，不定非等到批件后在办，这样时间太久，如果着急买机票可以先办个空证（估计都要十五工作日拿下来），拿到批件再去办后续。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.当然推荐台北新北的学校，一来交通十分便利，二来文化经济中心想看的很多博物馆演出展览都在那里。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Norya</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：605741512</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvbzfGue0ponzxFb7XRev7jZEfg5vyeNicLxfRqMtkm41oMznQ6ICZnJg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7509881422924901\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"677px\" class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvbzfGue0ponzxFb7XRev7jZEfg5vyeNicLxfRqMtkm41oMznQ6ICZnJg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">Aven Young:</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、我是经历了一次小小的考试再加上平时的综合成绩成为一名台湾交换生，所以也没有经历过面试什么的吧…^_^ 2、前期的话，好像主要是根据台湾国际学生处老师的要求准备登记照、身份证、户口之类的，要邮寄过去，推荐顺丰，比较快而且便宜～然后就是体检啦！每个学校要求不一样，如果要求比较严格一点的，一般医院做不了，就得去出入境检验检疫局那里做全身体检 3、入台证照片一定要按照对方学校老师的要求，格式、大小、还有面部要求之类的，以及之后核对信息一定要细心！ 4、理工科的同学建议申请台大、台清华、台交大、云林科技、逢甲、中山…人文类的同学我推荐政大、成大、台师大、辅仁、中央…这仅仅是我的了解啦～可供参考 台北是个景点丰富、商圈云集、集结各国美味又有文艺范儿的城市，如果不想走远…半年了解台北一座城也是非常值得的！ 台中城比较小，但交通极为便利，贯通南北，去哪边都很方便，最美大学东海大学与恶作剧之吻的拍摄地静宜大学都是好去处，还有十公里内免费的台中公交真心节省了一大笔车费！ 南部去的比较少…所以没什么经验可以给大家分享啦！</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：Aven-YXW</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fv57eJEicicHiaQrzpYKMJTtjz4nDSic4JQFeVhEOicic9KVbeMToWDXGlxbFA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" class=\"\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7509881422924901\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fv57eJEicicHiaQrzpYKMJTtjz4nDSic4JQFeVhEOicic9KVbeMToWDXGlxbFA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 733.6px; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">叶彦祖：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.面试经历:我们老师问的问题涉及到学业相关，对台湾的了解度还有跟台湾相关的敏感问题等好几个方面。学业方面是要了解自己专业的修课计划，提前想好自己到台湾要选的课程，以及对于在台湾自己想做的事情要心里有数。老师还有问为什么想要去台湾交换，这个问题不要太直白地说去玩，总之给一个稍微有道理的答案。老师会假设一些棘手的生活情况让回答怎么办，这个就随机应变了，回答的话原则上就是不参与政治活动，不与台湾同学起冲突。我们学校有笔试，有道坑爹的题是向台湾同学介绍自己学校（...）。我就随便一说哈哈哈。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.城市学校专业推荐:去台北 去台北 去台北（来自一个来了俩月还没找到机会去台北的二逼少女的真诚建议）。然后选课，如果想要出去玩，星期一或者星期五一定不要选课。台湾的假期最多三天（下半年），这种假还没几次，如果一个礼拜选满了又不想逃课的话，想去远一点的地方玩就基本没戏了。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">其他建议:口味重的比如喜欢吃辣的同学，慎重考虑一下来台交换这个事。当然可能是我实在是不能适应，总之是台湾美食半点不对我胃口（湖南人），现在天天不知道吃什么，分分钟觉得自己要饿死在这边。真的，真的。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：lalalala1995</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fv1dcgpnE90fNvJ4y1RL39w9fK5ichyGt9znlzjMYZVhVvS4qyhk4td4Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.6679841897233202\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"677px\" class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fv1dcgpnE90fNvJ4y1RL39w9fK5ichyGt9znlzjMYZVhVvS4qyhk4td4Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">Aileen Chan:</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Hello，学弟妹们或者同学们，你们好呀！我是今年秋季赴台交换学习的孩纸。台湾这个宝岛相信大家对他憧憬了很久，甚至可能有同学已经去过了。但是和去台湾玩相比，去台湾学习是另外一种体验，下面让我来分享一下经验吧：）</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">☆首先呢是入台面试。入台面试前，我一直觉得会很难，但后来得知因为申请时间紧迫，老师说可以不用面试，跟我们召集会议简单介绍自己之后就可以了。其实无论什么面试，放轻松点，不要紧张就可以，这也是学长姐告诉我的他们的入台面试经验。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">☆在申请的前期，首先把自己原来学校的功课完成好，然后呢你要有一个对台湾热爱的心，其次询问父母的意见，与家人讨论是否愿意让您到台湾交换学习，最后呢，就是要准备一颗可以边学习边享受宝岛的美的心♡</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">☆在申请的过程中，很多人都会遇到许多问题，比方说：这个学校的系部到底符不符合我原本学校所在的系（或专业）〔Tips：要选择与自己原本学校相符合的专业〕；亦或是入台证通行证的办理需要什么数据〔Tips：照片，电子表和纸质表，照片回执…〕……遇到申请中的问题不要紧，相信在申请的过程中，老师肯定会给很多宝贵的意见或是推荐，重点就是大家只要按学校老师说的步骤，一步一步地完成申请的程序，一般都会没有问题的！BTW，有什么不明白的记得问老师或者问有经验的学长姐（当然我也可以啦( •̀∀•́ )）</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">☆下面我来介绍一下我在交换学习的学校啦( •̀∀•́ )我是一个在高雄市的义守大学中读应用英语系的孩纸。义守大学是座美丽的城堡，你会被它美丽的夜景吸引；被它高大的建筑吸引；甚至是被老师跟同学的亲切吸引♡若是有想要到义守大学交换的孩纸们，欢迎你们的到来，有什么疑问都欢迎来问我喔：）</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">☆最后，希望所有向往宝岛的大家都可以申请到自己喜欢的学校，祝你们成功喔！</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：Alieenchan</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvLxIR8OAeTHxzRwCoca3LU42hYsHwsMcqDGqjGZxCZHFicSFD8CsSiapw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" class=\"\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7509881422924901\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvLxIR8OAeTHxzRwCoca3LU42hYsHwsMcqDGqjGZxCZHFicSFD8CsSiapw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 733.6px; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">王擎：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">来自一个普通家庭，普通学生的台湾交换生自身经历。首先，关于入台面试经历，现在想想真是挺波折的，因为是学校第一次有这种交流机会，自己想报名又犹豫不决，和父母商量后，父亲不同意，因为自然会认为这样花很多钱，我想如果家庭像我一样的父亲都会这样想，怕要交很多钱，毕竟家庭不富裕，母亲倒是支持，最后是在上海姑姑的极力劝说下，父亲勉强同意了，在这里我想说，找个有更多经历的人寻求建议是多么重要，父亲没文化所以都反对，真的要感谢我的姑姑才能坚定我来台湾，最后再说关于面试，成绩一般，但是我态度很好，因为平常就是很爱聊天，很所有评审老师交流很好，最后老师还说这个小伙子很不错，高兴坏我了。其次关于准备，证件这些老师都会帮你弄好，只是入台证要本人去办理，提醒一下，如果家很远的同学最好在入台证办理好后再回家，因为当时我们7月3号暑假我就回家了，老师建议我们先留下来可是没有，后面过了2个星期只能再回学校，真的很麻烦，建议办理完再回家。申请过程最重要的我觉得就是你开朗的性格，这真的很重要。不要害羞，和评审老师唠嗑就行了，哈哈我就是这样，做ppt很重要，当时很多人没做ppt介绍自己，做了的很加分，因为毕竟大家都是新生，还不懂做ppt正式介绍。我是南京医科大学，预防医学专业的学生，我想说，如果你在考虑要不要来交换，真的一定要来，应该说当时最后问了星竹姐，更坚定自己了。我建议那些家庭普通或者没有那么好的同学更要来，真的更要来，因为我们以后因为家庭因素，基本不能留学，这倒是真的，所以来台湾交换真的是非常好的机会，真的，他会让我们不断的重新看待自己，调整的价值观，好像有点吹大了，哈哈，不过确实这样。一点不夸张，最后我想建议一下来台湾交换的同学们，我想说，你们代表大陆同学，真的希望你们做好自己，有次在花莲和一群交换生坐一辆车游玩，她们有些行为习惯真的有些让人看不下去了，真的有种自己和他们一样作为交换生感到好丢脸，台湾同学，阿姨真的很好，真的希望你们做好自己，提升自己，感受交换，我相信你们真的能得到感受很多，哈哈。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：Barnett-WQ</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvPd2lolyhuPJNndudfkzkSvrcsSxcibM6yHuhIT899VcyzYMedTo8Urg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7509881422924901\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"677px\" class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvPd2lolyhuPJNndudfkzkSvrcsSxcibM6yHuhIT899VcyzYMedTo8Urg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">匿名：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.面试的话我们是基本按学分绩来录取，所以就是走走形式…</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.前期就是刷高学分绩啦…</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3.申请过程中台湾的手续还是很复杂的，但是一般给出的文件会写得很清楚，大家仔细阅读就好，自己不看就去问国际合作处的老师会被骂很惨…</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.学校的选择，如果你是要好好学习，千万千万不要来台北！不要来台北！交通太发达，诱惑太多，完全把持不住！最后就沦为像我一样天天吃吃吃玩玩玩…而我在新竹交大和清大的同学因为去哪都不方便就每天专心做学问哎哎哎…</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">金老汉：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先，十分感谢美女主页妞Pansey的邀请。我在2013年秋季和2015年春季分別申请赴台交换，两次都顺利拿到入台邀请信，但前者因为个人原因未能成行。我觉得在台湾交换更适合二年级的本科生，一方面友好的台湾与大陆一衣带水，语言文字相通，适应起来并不困难，另一方面即使本来学校的课程上因为赴台有所拖欠也可以在接下来的大三来弥补。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于学校，自然是因人而异。对于出国党，可能专业对口、综合实力强的名校为佳，台成清交这样的名校交换经历对出国无疑加分，教授的海外背景写成的推荐信也是很可贵的；对于一心追求游学体验的同学，倒不妨选择自己喜欢的、课程压力小一点的学校，好多出一些时间出去走一走，挑一个出行方便、物价适中、校园美丽、男女比例适合自己的学校更好。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我所在的大陆母校与台湾的高校合作密切，与国立中央大学更是同根同源，每学期都有40+的同学赴台交换至十余所学校，所以申请难度不大。学校会在综合考虑在校成绩排名、外语水平、笔试成绩与个人志愿的基础上做出分配，笔试会考台湾的历史地理风土人情与政治经济，比如现任总统这样的题目，也没有特別的面试。申请过程中填写表格按部就班就好，早一点订好机票省钱省心。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">讲一点个人的经验，申请交换的同学，可以早作安排，让自己的男女朋友办理自由行甚至结伴交换，一起在台湾游玩，是不错的恋爱回忆；出国党可以在台湾考托福与GRE，费用会稍便宜一点，场次考位充裕，但需要办理护照与双币种结算的信用卡；最后说一点，真的很希望台湾能允许大陆在台湾的交换生、学位生在台湾工读。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：asl</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvoJvSdYOGBJOFiaxKrGv015JbKqFdVCwLE3KzmTSoDjib9iaV3oBS4dLrw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" class=\"\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7509881422924901\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvoJvSdYOGBJOFiaxKrGv015JbKqFdVCwLE3KzmTSoDjib9iaV3oBS4dLrw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 733.6px; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: inherit; border: 0px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">柯乐乐：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.入台面试经历：我的经验是不需要在面试中讲的天花乱坠，因为我的材料交上去面试官一个问题都没问就让我下去了，而我前面一个女生讲了将近20分钟，但她没进，我认为主要原因是他的专业不对口，面试过程中面试官较注重现实因素，如你的专业对口性，你的导师是否同意（我是硕士）等硬性的条件。2.前期准备。学习计划这些书面材料。3.注意事项。同一。4.我是教育方面的，台湾教育的大学不多，推荐台北市的，台湾师范大学，以及其他师范、教育大学。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：kelele0965</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19.125px; color: rgb(6, 117, 11);\">邱霞燕：</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们来台交换不用面试也不用笔试，就交一份简历就好(基本按绩点和人数来)，办证学校也会帮忙，所以前期就没什么经验 至于学校的话，我会稍微考虑学校的全球排名、学校风景；专业的话因为提前知道选课可以跨学院跨专业跨年级，所以专业还是按照自己的兴趣，但是选课的时候会选可以转换学分的课，不可以转的就会旁听，所以专业也不会有很多疑惑；城市选择有两个，一是要和大陆差异比较大的，二是交通要便利。</section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">微信号：Swallow_Qiu</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; width: 733.6px; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvLK6aCKyN92fFxqBIichlQAXAwxaqCCbjcDv1A5qxHUAkDWcuGyoVAyg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.7509881422924901\" data-w=\"\" _width=\"677px\" class=\"\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JdCyxVHsYYJYGcUsLzQQzmT7SibtA04fvLK6aCKyN92fFxqBIichlQAXAwxaqCCbjcDv1A5qxHUAkDWcuGyoVAyg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"/> <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> <section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/> </section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 10